result:
<v-navigation-drawer
      class="sidebar hidden-md-and-up"
      hide-overlay
      app
       :style="customStyle"
       dark
       touchless
       v-model="navigation" >

       <v-divider></v-divider>
       
      <v-list class="pt-0">
      <template v-for="item in items">
      <v-list-tile
        :key="item.title"
        :to="item.path"
        @click="navigation=false"
        class="white--text"
      >
        <v-list-tile-action>
          <v-icon color="white">{{ item.icon }}</v-icon>
        </v-list-tile-action>

        <v-list-tile-content class="white--text">
          <v-list-tile-title>{{ item.title }}</v-list-tile-title>
        </v-list-tile-content>
      </v-list-tile>
      
    </template>
  </v-list>
</v-navigation-drawer>
